/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/John_Forbes_Nash\" title=\"John Forbes Nash\" class=\"mw-redirect\">John Nash<\/a> and <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Reinhard_Selten\" title=\"Reinhard Selten\">Reinhard Selten<\/a> of the 1994 <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Nobel_Prize_in_Economics\" title=\"Nobel Prize in Economics\" class=\"mw-redirect\">Nobel Memorial Prize in Economics<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"John Harsanyi","place_of_birth":"Budapest ,  Hungary","place_of_death":"Berkeley, California ,  USA","text":"John Harsanyi , Economics, 1994","year":1994.0}